{"title":"香溪桔歌","authors":["欣秋"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"香溪桔歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣　秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国的“嘉树”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，柑桔林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，南国的“嘉树”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的枝叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金色的果实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这群山之中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片片，一层层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“青黄杂糅”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多好的一幅“金碧山水”图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得儿时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读过《桔颂》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从“绿叶素荣”的诗丛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾窥到三闾大夫沉思中的气骨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日，再看眼前："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人面金橙，笑语欢歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昭君村的儿女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正把一腔豪情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向柑桔林倾注！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月橙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月橙，五月橙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个头儿不高，一蓬蓬矮林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既缺少自身应有的妩媚姌袅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又没有柑桔姐妹那般风貌娉婷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，她却有一颗金子似的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那样朴实，那样忠贞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当一场秋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉了所有的蜜桔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也醉了其它的柑橙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有她，五月橙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还那般自持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸儿不红，身影儿端正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她守着自己的本份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不和姐妹们去赶热闹，争宠于人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一当春风从冰雪中走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的心便开始萌动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一当爱情成熟了的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便跑着、跳着向她所爱的献身！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}